'''Doctor''' may refer to:
* [[Medical Doctor]]s, the main doctors who can be consulted and treat a variety of diseases and ailments.
* [[Alternative Doctor]]s, special types of doctors who can treat certain diseases or ailments.
* [[Psychiatrist]],  a doctor who specialises in mental therapy for emotional health.
* [[Optometrist]], an eye doctor who provides glasses to change up your character's look.
* [[Witch Doctor]], a doctor whose spells and concoctions can treat you, but may harm you as well.
